{"tid":318794,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇正嘅英文歌推介","createTime":"2017-07-12T10:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T20:26:27.000Z","uid":96778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"af9b06240100371ab02339b16136f31d96a5b912","tid":318794,"uid":96778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:49:03.000Z","msg":"想要啲冷門少少嘅，唔想成日聽黎聽下都係最hit個啲<br />\n最好歌詞有啲意思啦，咩類型啲歌都想聽下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"addf78e5f64437ed6f5f3ca6c7b9039b6a5fd85d","tid":318794,"uid":69120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:50:54.000Z","msg":"19 + you and me <br />\npop 美國後生仔情歌 無咩人聽但好q 正<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/S-Ac3uVAPZY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS-Ac3uVAPZY&d=G4ubfc8puRVWXimNTO3Q58n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=000a3a40\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/S-Ac3uVAPZY</a>"},{"pid":"982c14fbaa7e893a8fd0c7f6c648a126d5364c92","tid":318794,"uid":31172,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:53:14.000Z","msg":"the national - apartment story<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/S97xQKZDV_4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FS97xQKZDV_4&d=G4ubfc8puRVWXimNTO3Q58n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=60141a05\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/S97xQKZDV_4</a><br />\n<br />\nthe national - pink rabbit<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/tCEr4XbyLR8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtCEr4XbyLR8&d=G4ubfc8puRVWXimNTO3Q58n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=5b70294c\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/tCEr4XbyLR8</a><br />\n<br />\nthe national - mistaken for strangers<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/cgRsYkKb1eI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcgRsYkKb1eI&d=G4ubfc8puRVWXimNTO3Q58n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=633a90df\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/cgRsYkKb1eI</a>"},{"pid":"ec7efd41d2d40f81376364e2f3496236b0a3dd0b","tid":318794,"uid":37168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:53:43.000Z","msg":"聽The Script"},{"pid":"0076e8f300ed1cd2905289f785d57b5aff90d77e","tid":318794,"uid":55511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:59:26.000Z","msg":"(黎自我好耐之前寫的一個post）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7oday_Fc-Gc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7oday_Fc-Gc&d=G4ubfc8puRVWXimNTO3Q58n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=7cd36233\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7oday_Fc-Gc</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nY8uEYsFoJs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnY8uEYsFoJs&d=G4ubfc8puRVWXimNTO3Q58n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=f70d83f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nY8uEYsFoJs</a><br />\n好耐之前伍公子啲片引用過 <br />\n首歌好聽好特別之餘 聽聞係黎自一套電影 Sacco e Vanzetti(1971) 源自真實歷史<br />\n講述兩個意大利人 Nicola Sacco ， Bartolomeo Vanzetti 係20年代既美國牽涉一單搶劫同謀殺案 雖然證據不足 佢地仍因為受種族歧視同政治運動(無政府主義信仰)被法院誤判死刑<br />\n發來引起公眾極大的回響 輿論傳媒既報導 有人想佢地去死 亦有各地既人為S,V上街抗議<br />\n但係死刑仍然係8月22日 1927年以電椅執行<br />\n<br />\n係四月既時候 Sacco釋出咁樣既confession<br />\n<blockquote>I would not wish to a dog or to a snake, to the most low and misfortunate creature of the earth, I would not wish to any of them what I have had to suffer for things that I am not guilty of. But my conviction is that I have suffered for things that I am guilty of. I am suffering because I am a radical and indeed I am a radical; I have suffered because I am an Italian and indeed I am an Italian...if you could execute me two times, and if I could be reborn two other times, I would live again to do what I have done already.</blockquote><br />\n類似對白令我諗番起tyrion lannister既trail<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/e4Uq8O5ZhUA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fe4Uq8O5ZhUA&d=G4ubfc8puRVWXimNTO3Q58n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=27b4f69c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/e4Uq8O5ZhUA</a><br />\n<br />\n一個人係咩身份已經令到佢架上一個罪行<br />\n<br />\n而係Sacco e Vanzetti呢套電影既六年之後 <br />\nSV死後既五十年之後 當初上街遊行既人，<br />\n寫報紙既人，審錯案既法官，辯護律師，同埋真心覺得佢地係抵死既人 都差唔多死晒之後<br />\n1977年 麻省法院最終宣佈兩人既無罪 洗去佢地既污名<br />\n<br />\n咁樣一段故事 轉化做幾句歌詞<br />\nHere's to you niccola and bart<br />\nRest forever here in our heart<br />\nThe last and final moment is yours, <br />\nthe agony is your triumph<br />\n<br />\n聽完引發人思考既係 <br />\n其實佢係咪只不過 今天我 既英文版<br />\n所謂勝利係咪只不過精神上<br />\n係S同V 我淨係睇到受苦，其他人亦唔見得有報應，<br />\n睇番最近香港因為政治運動被拘捕既一炸人<br />\n其實佢地爭取緊既係咩呢? 而家既我地又到底值唔值呢?"},{"pid":"b8623ce46cd717a7a6a8790d305fd8154a7a7d7a","tid":318794,"uid":96778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T20:16:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fe20dea760238a0bed0d315d8824b6a2fd7e3c5b","tid":318794,"uid":14675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T20:24:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JU1jx973iqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJU1jx973iqs&d=G4ubfc8puRVWXimNTO3Q58n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=0f039ba6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JU1jx973iqs</a>"},{"pid":"58b7723ea932d8a55f7925747904a84b7e35a0f1","tid":318794,"uid":58246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T20:26:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/K9FILAkKinQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FK9FILAkKinQ&d=G4ubfc8puRVWXimNTO3Q58n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=24933c93\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/K9FILAkKinQ</a>"}]}